{{Top|leg}}
The '''Eye of the Pirate''' was a red [[Star/Legends|star]] visible in the sky of [[Corellia/Legends|Corellia]]. It was connected to the constellations of the [[Drall's Hat]] and [[the Ronto]].

{{Star-stub}}

==Behind the scenes==
[[Jason Fry]], co-author of ''[[The Essential Atlas]]'', indicated in [[June]] [[2015]] that the Eye of the Pirate was excluded from [[Star Wars: The Essential Atlas Online Companion|''The Essential Atlas'' Online Companion]] because it was a local name for a visible star, and not its commonly accepted name.<ref name="Email">{{EmailCite|email=File:EAOC discussion.jpg|creator=Jason Fry|date=2015-06-30}}</ref>

